description.displayText:
Jillian babysat regularly for my three young children (3, 6, 7) in Long Island. They always talked about how much fun they had when Jillian would babysit. She'd take them to the park, out for ice cream and would even help with online school (because I can never figure that out). 

It was also always great to come home to a tidy home. Though my husband and I never asked her to clean, Jillian would always wash the dishes and organize toys before leaving.
